{"tid":831669,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"港大膳食服務重整 新餐廳唔收現金","createTime":"2018-09-22T06:57:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-22T15:23:41.000Z","uid":164435,"like":21,"dislike":128,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"fb9fd5c21bef03e996384f4d7cc01741e34205fd","tid":831669,"uid":164435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T06:57:12.000Z","msg":"【明報專訊】香港大學學生發展及資源中心（CEDARS）噚日用電郵向學生公布校園膳食服務重組後嘅開業日期，入面提到新開業餐廳將唔會接受現金交易，同學都要用電子貨幣交易，包括 Visa、Master、八達通、Apple Pay、Android Pay，而微信支付（WeChat Pay）同支付寶（Alipay）將來亦會包括在內。<br />\n<br />\n涉至少4間餐廳<br />\n<br />\n港大話，因為近年現金增值儲值卡同電子支付普及，學校同膳食承辦商協議之後，決定新開業餐廳唔接受現金交易，提升「餐廳服務效率並為顧客提供更便捷的服務」。<br />\n<br />\n今次涉及嘅餐廳最少有成4間咁多！學校就話，餐廳開業之後，校方會根據顧客嘅反應同措施實行嘅順暢程度再檢視一吓。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20180922/s00002/1537553797617\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180922%2Fs00002%2F1537553797617&d=v8KQLTnareU90bbLtfNQZOargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=84b6311b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180922%2Fs00002%2F1537553797617&h=c82d7932\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20180922/s00002/1537553797617</a>"},{"pid":"8e226abb6e3719f92bc1d2dbebbd310449c98d11","tid":831669,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T06:58:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a3bd41dc06de149368e3cc8f28ef72a2c16d2bf","tid":831669,"uid":164435,"like":109,"dislike":2,"score":107,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T07:00:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote> <span style=\"color: red;\">Android Pay</span> </blockquote><br />\n其實人哋改咗名做Google Pay<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://pay.google.com/about/static/images/social/og_image.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpay.google.com%2Fabout%2Fstatic%2Fimages%2Fsocial%2Fog_image.jpg&h=fabca6bb&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"6027d22698de391279ec178cddaa54843bd86bac","tid":831669,"uid":693,"like":3,"dislike":23,"score":-20,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T07:02:44.000Z","msg":"現金唔係法定付款單位咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3767711febcdb0f22953af4d47ab2e3fe8d5a306","tid":831669,"uid":198622,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T07:03:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7b7dc35befa0e7781a40f4ace21152b0372ada81","tid":831669,"uid":41368,"like":4,"dislike":15,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T07:03:28.000Z","msg":"以後要拎學生資料就更容易<br />\n你班大麻撚等pk"},{"pid":"ef6c6581909810946bbe50ed7afd145b471ab753","tid":831669,"uid":164435,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"quote":{"pid":"6027d22698de391279ec178cddaa54843bd86bac","tid":831669,"uid":693,"like":3,"dislike":23,"score":-20,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T07:02:44.000Z","msg":"現金唔係法定付款單位咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T07:03:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201001/20/P201001200090.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201001%2F20%2FP201001200090.htm&d=v8KQLTnareU90bbLtfNQZOargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=d4e28d19\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201001/20/P201001200090.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n（一）根據現行《法定貨幣紙幣發行條例》及《硬幣條例》所發行的紙幣和硬幣均為香港的法定貨幣。作為法定貨幣，它是一種有效和合法的支付媒介，在法律上被視為可充分及有效地履行支付義務。然而，在任何商業交易中，交易雙方均可自行決定交易條款，包括決定使用何等支付媒介。對商品和服務供應商而言，是否接受任何面額的紙幣和硬幣以支付某項交易純粹是他們的商業決定。我們亦曾對其他國家就「法定貨幣」的法例和行使方法作出研究。據我們了解，在大多數國家包括英國、加拿大、澳洲、美國和新加坡等地，均有「法定貨幣」的條例以確立當地貨幣的法定地位，但並沒有強制當地居民或商品和服務供應商必須接受當地法定貨幣作為支付媒介或設立罰則來懲罰拒收者。在該等國家，買賣雙方可以自行決定支付的媒介，所以香港與上述國家的情況相若。"},{"pid":"4b684bd22da74caa8ac872873c6903e966738f43","tid":831669,"uid":164435,"like":12,"dislike":3,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"3767711febcdb0f22953af4d47ab2